channel.title: Some icons [Updated with proof]
channel.description:
Ok, so Im a leecher eh? Check this out you, im no fraud like most people so imma give yall a reward for your effort:
Heres the proof you all need since you think I STOLE this shit, although I admit I didn't pay attention to the home one that I posted (I thought it was this one: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/home-1.png[/img]): Step 1: First I open up MS Paint & make a image then copy it - I could give anyone here a guide on how to pixel if they wanted: http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/copying.jpg
Step 2: After doing step one I paste my image to gimp: http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/pasted.jpg
Step 3: Then after pasting I cut out the black part of the image so that it become transparent: http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/cuttedun-neededshit.jpg
Step 4: After cutting the unneeded stuff out I go to the crop image menu so I can crop it: http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/croppingimage.jpg
Step 5: After i hit the crop command I get this for the outcome: http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/imagecropped.jpg
Step 6: And then I save it: http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/saving.jpg
Step 7: Now I shall put the fatality move down called "Owned Big Time!" on the make-belief-poster nerd(s) down below: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/biggreyanddarksiliconborder-1.png[/img]
[hr]
I know these may not sound like much but to me they are, and I am currently learning to make them so umm.. Yeah, I don't use any sophisticated program like photoshop or gimp for my icons, but instead I use MS Paint.
Download icon for website templates & stuff: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/Download.png[/img]
just plain-o'paper icon for like about & contact pages or probbaly login & register..: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/Info.png[/img]
Home icon: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/home-1.png[/img]
Message icon or just quote a quote for news papers & stuff: [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/Message.png[/img]
Statistic for like your website traffic & stuff... [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/Statistic.png[/img]
And icon for templates ya know, I just thought about it since I've never seen no one do it before... [IMG]http://i260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/template.png[/img]
